I have been visiting Dr Sanchi Chabbra for dental treatment for the past nearly one year . I must say that Dr Sanchi is very professional with her work. She makes you very comfortable throughout the treatment and has a very genuine concern for her patient's dental health.

She is a very pleasant doctor and describes the entire procedure in depth with patience and is very accommodative with the appointments and scheduling. The best treatment for the patient is actually practiced in the clinic very ethically at the most reasonable cost feasible. Her clinic in Defence Colony has a very fine ambience and cleanliness. 

I must say that being a retired Army Colonel I am entitled to free Dental treatment at Army Dental clinics/ECHS empaneled clinics but still I prefer to undertake Dental treatment from Dr Sanchi because of her professionalism and dedication towards her patients. 

I strongly recommend her to anyone looking for good dental care in New Delhi/ NCR. She has excellent staff, like Ms. Kajal at the Reception and good clinical assistant too. Thank you Dr Sanchi Chabbra.

Dr. Sanchi is so good with her work. One is made comfortable through out the treatment. Professional ism at the same time combined with genuine concern for your dental health added with the expertise in her area is a rare find now a days. 
What is actually needed and what is best for you is actually practiced in the clinic which has such a good ambience as well as a clean and a comfortable feel. 
I don't think me and my family can go anywhere else, even if we have to travel all the way from Gurgaon. 

A Sure Recommend to all! 

Thank You always Doctor!

My mom had a fall over her face , her entire denture was in bad  shape . She treated them all with lots and lots of  patience  keeping her age in mind giving her least amount of pain .  

She is available at all times . She is an excellent dentist I have known so far . 

Thank you  doctor

Dr Sanchi is patient, dedicated to her work and extremely mindful of the patient throughout the procedure. I highly recommend her to anyone looking for the best dental care in New Delhi. She alao has excellent staff, like Ms Kajal and her clinical assistant too.
Highly amicable.. described the entire procedure in depth and was very accommodative with the appointments and scheduling
As always it's pleasure to go to her clinic . She is a master of her craft. She fully explains the procedure she is doing. Would 100 percent recommend her.

survey_response.review_text:
Doctor is expert in her work and humble in dealing. 
The clinic is very clean and well designed. 
Explaining the issue of doctor is very good.

*** ****** *** ********** I explained that I was nervous and hadn't been to the dentist for a long time due to my fear. She listened to what I had to say, and spoke to me about what was causing my fear to try to understand it better. She took the time to do a proper examination and explained fully the treatment I needed. She talked me through every step of the treatment and on a number of occasions during the treatment asked if I was alright. After being scared to go to the dentist for so long, I couldn't have had a better experience. I was put at ease from the moment I walked through the door till the moment I walked out. I can honestly say that I don't feel as worried about going to the dentist again. I couldn't recommend Dr. Sanchi Chhabra highly enough.

I recently went to see Dr Sanchi at Nanda Dental clinic thinking that I have a case of receding gums as I could feel a gap between one of my teeth and gums. She was very friendly, examined my teeth patiently and explained that it was actually not a case of receding gums, but a cavity due to application of excessive pressure during brushing. She fixed it in 15 mins with a filing (almost painless) and I was good to go! She also explained how to care for it going forward. Would highly recommend to everyone!

The entire experience of the treatment for getting a 3 teeth bridge fitting was very pleasant and smooth. The work was done by Dr Sanchi very efficiently and to my satisfaction. I have already started recommending her to my friends and acquaintances
